  m_Name: 5 calambra
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  planet: 5
  descriptions:
  - 'Calambara is a desert planet where the majority of the population live underground
    due to the extreme heat on the surface. '
  - 'Their bodies are extremely good at conserving temperature. Calambara is also
    in the same solar system as Kaaman, where the game of ArrowHex originated, which
    gives them a vast history of playing this ancient game. '
  - 'They even won the intergalactic championship twice. Some even theorize that
    they could have been one of the best planets if only they had a larger population. '
  - The harsh conditions on their planet result in a much smaller population.
